test.java.com.hexcore.vrmeeting_hostserver.mock

Class MockDataServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • test.java.com.hexcore.vrmeeting_hostserver.mock.MockDataServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataServerConnector

    public class MockDataServer
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataServerConnector
    A mock DataServerConnector used in testing Has the ability to change whether retrieveUserData(String) throws an exception due to an invalid token and retreiveMeetingData(String) throws an exception due to an invalid meeting id Also whether either will throw an exception due to the data server being 'unavailable' By default the server is available and all tokens and meetingid are valid A defualt test user is returned unless an alternative is provided in the constructor
    Author:
    Psymj1 (Marcus)
